
flowchart TD
    A[Enter: subsystem, reason, sub_reason] --> B[Read STM_TIM0, STM_CAP, STM_CLC]
    B --> C[Save scaled timers to crash record at 0xD000DF30]
    C --> D[Save caller return address]
    D --> E[Save reason and its bitwise inverse]
    E --> F[Save sub_reason and subsystem id]
    F --> G{Debugger bit set in DBGSR?}
    G -->|Yes| H[Halt to OCDS debugger]
    G -->|No| I[Continue]
    H --> J[Unlock watchdog with password pattern]
    I --> J
    J --> K[Re-lock watchdog with new config]
    K --> L[Write RST_REQ = 4]
    L --> M[Spin forever until reset fires]